{"tid":1426893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔必須承認既事 駁唔到","createTime":"2019-08-07T04:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T04:23:14.000Z","uid":5822,"like":7,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8add1051d246d365aaac69bd20cebdf2f5e5adf4","tid":1426893,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:14:37.000Z","msg":"前線做既野的確係踐踏緊法治同法律<br />\n的確係破壞左公物 <br />\n的確係有擾民 <br />\n的確係有前線失控 <br />\n同埋被捕人士一定唔會無條件釋放返出黎<br />\n<br />\n大家都支持示威運動 但以上幾點係毫無疑問<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過黑警而家係摧毁緊法治 並無任何代價係毫無疑問</span> 政權更是支持摧毀法治人士逍遙法外係絕對唔可以容忍 <br />\n<br />\n連登好多po講出黎既野唔係割蓆 係想大家安全同改善以不被捕為首要 請大家先睇左再思考可能性 唔可以得個勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見住拉咁多人真係唔好受"},{"pid":"01e78a3eadc455af5a98b198bb3c92d07f6c2c71","tid":1426893,"uid":35005,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:19:10.000Z","msg":"左膠<br />\n買觀星筆都破壞法治啦而家<br />\n仲講呢D"},{"pid":"60b0c354cb0057d3335aa8fcbff96216328f83b4","tid":1426893,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01e78a3eadc455af5a98b198bb3c92d07f6c2c71","tid":1426893,"uid":35005,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:19:10.000Z","msg":"左膠<br />\n買觀星筆都破壞法治啦而家<br />\n仲講呢D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:20:03.000Z","msg":"幾時有講呢單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78edf3440a8eaab5a18e1e9052b196dc291600dd","tid":1426893,"uid":25213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:22:33.000Z","msg":"咁計法，二戰搶灘都犯左偷渡啦"},{"pid":"e7dcd12ed79eed127714e69f722cb72ac7ca42d1","tid":1426893,"uid":29132,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:22:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">著名五毛 負評 上一頁 完</span></span>"},{"pid":"90dfcbd32ed1f36be4f7979a9a5b2b6eacc06baa","tid":1426893,"uid":294844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:23:14.000Z","msg":"違法達義"}]}